articles.title: Britons accuse EU of 'backdoor' tactics to wreck Brexit 'Can't let them get away with it!' - Express
articles.description: THE British public strongly support Northern Ireland remaining part of the United Kingdom, according to new polling which reveals sharp concern that the actions of the European Union are a threat to peace in the province.
